      "description": "Validation result comparing FEA-predicted construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement against N=11 experimental constructs. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-specified acceptance criterion (<10% mean difference, E/uval < 1.96). The ModelConfiguration used for this run was tagged ansys-mechanical-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, the release candidate immediately preceding the released build. The simulation team confirmed that no solver kernel changes were introduced between rc2 and the final build-7 release; only documentation and installer metadata differed. On this basis the result is considered directly applicable to the current model of record without re-execution.",
