        "name": "Ansys Mechanical 2026 Q1 Build 7 Release Candidate 2",
        "modelVersion": "ansys-mechanical-2026-q1-build-7-rc2",
        "description": "Ansys Mechanical structural solver configured for implicit nonlinear static analysis of the ASTM F1717 pedicle screw construct. Titanium alloy Ti-6Al-4V material card (bilinear isotropic hardening, E=114 GPa, σ_y=880 MPa) applied to screw and rod; UHMWPE block modeled as neo-Hookean hyperelastic. Frictional contact (μ=0.25) at screw-rod interface. Mesh: ~310 000 quadratic tetrahedral elements, average element size 0.18 mm in thread region. This configuration corresponds to the release candidate immediately preceding the official 2026-Q1 build-7 release; the team assessed the delta as documentation-only and did not re-execute validation under the released binary."
      }
