    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) is below required level due to single-condition testing; residual risk is accepted given medium model influence, medium decision consequence, and supporting analytical sensitivity analysis. E/uval values for all three QoIs fall below 1.96, satisfying the pre-specified quantitative acceptance criterion. The validation result was generated under ModelConfiguration ansys-mechanical-2026-q1-build-7-rc2; the assessment team confirmed that no solver kernel changes were introduced between rc2 and the released ansys-mechanical-2026-q1-build-7 build, and on this basis the result is considered applicable to the current model of record. Overall credibility is sufficient for Medium assurance level at model risk level 3.",
